name: Have you heard of the high elves?
name_original: Have you heard of the high elves?
description:
By Ivan Parkhomenko, Dylan Kirkby and Brian Cowan

A lone elf teleported to a sky island via haywire portal – you have survived this long with just your kettle and the apple trees. The two portals here are linked to each other, but you might see equal luck to your prior lack of!
